hat Olympic event halfway around the world to the South Pacific country of French Polynesia.\", \"from\": 236, \"to\": 345, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that Olympic event\", \"from\": 252, \"to\": 270}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 295}, {\"ngram\": \"the South Pacific country\", \"from\": 299, \"to\": 324}, {\"ngram\": \"French Polynesia\", \"from\": 328, \"to\": 344}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes will compete on the island of Tahiti, in a small coastal village called Teahupo'o.\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 441, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 389, \"end\": 395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999998365224334, \"rank\": 1.6347765394389136e-07, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The athletes\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 358}, {\"ngram\": \"the island\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 385}, {\"ngram\": \"a small coastal village\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 423}, {\"ngram\": \"Teahupo'o\", \"from\": 431, \"to\": 440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The area is rural.\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 460, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The area\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 450}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It did not even have a road until the 1970s.\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 505, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a road\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hundreds of people are expected to visit Teahupo'o to watch the sport, as the surfers go out onto the famous waves from July 27 to August 4.\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 647, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hundreds\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 515}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 525}, {\"ngram\": \"Teahupo'o\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 557}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 567, \"to\": 576}, {\"ngram\": \"the surfers\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 592}, {\"ngram\": \"the famous waves\", \"from\": 605, \"to\": 621}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 631}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 644}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peva Levy is a Tahitian surfer.\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 680, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 664, \"end\": 672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999994512715289, \"rank\": 5.47945320761048e-07, \"text\": \"Tahitian\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peva Levy\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 658}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said the Teahupo'o beach was a \\\"secret spot\\\" when he first rode the waves there more than fifty years ago.\", \"from\": 681, \"to\": 790, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Teahupo'o beach\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 708}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"secret spot\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 727}, {\"ngram\": \"the waves\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 757}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But, he added, it did not stay secret.\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 829, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Teahupo'o gained fame among surfers around the world in the years since.\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 902, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fame\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 851}, {\"ngram\": \"surfers\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 865}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 882}, {\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 895}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Levy said the place has a special energy, a feeling known as \\\"mana\\\" in the local language.\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Levy\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 908}, {\"ngram\": \"the place\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 923}, {\"ngram\": \"a special energy\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 944}, {\"ngram\": \"a feeling\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 955}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"mana\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 970}, {\"ngram\": \"the local language\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 993}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the people who live there want that special quality protected.\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1062, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1010}, {\"ngram\": \"special quality\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are concerns that a week of Olympic competition in Teahupo'o could destroy the \\\"mana\\\" and harm the environment that surrounds it.\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1198, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"concerns\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1081}, {\"ngram\": \"a week\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1093}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic competition\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1116}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"mana\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1153}, {\"ngram\": \"the environment\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1179}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Proposed preparations for the event included building temporary housing, roads, and even a large structure out on the water.\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1324, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Proposed preparations\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1235}, {\"ngram\": \"temporary housing\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1271}, {\"ngram\": \"roads\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1278}, {\"ngram\": \"even a large structure\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1306}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The work called for drilling into acoral reef.\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1371, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The work\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1333}, {\"ngram\": \"acoral reef\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1370}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Opposition to the plans quickly grew.\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1409, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Opposition\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1382}, {\"ngram\": \"the plans\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1395}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Environmentalists, locals and surfers joined forces to protect Teahupo'o's culture, its corals and other sea life.\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1525, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Environmentalists\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1428}, {\"ngram\": \"locals\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1436}, {\"ngram\": \"surfers\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1448}, {\"ngram\": \"forces\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1462}, {\"ngram\": \"Teahupo'o's culture\", \"from\": 1474, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"its corals\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1505}, {\"ngram\": \"other sea life\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1524}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was too much for us, a big change,\\\" said Levy, who also serves on a local environmental organization Vai Ara o Teahupo'o.\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1652, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1632, \"end\": 1635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Vai\", \"score\": 0.9530752511166547, \"rank\": 0.04643129567304413, \"text\": \"Vai\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Vai\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Vai\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1550}, {\"ngram\": \"a big change\", \"from\": 1552, \"to\": 1564}, {\"ngram\": \"Levy\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1576}, {\"ngram\": \"a local environmental organization\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1631}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The group told the Olympic organizers they did not want new buildings or roads.\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1733, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The group\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1663}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic organizers\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1691}, {\"ngram\": \"new buildings\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1723}, {\"ngram\": \"roads\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1732}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And organizers are adjusting their plans as a result.\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1787, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"organizers\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1748}, {\"ngram\": \"their plans\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1774}, {\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For example, they will not be building any Olympic housing.\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1848, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1800}, {\"ngram\": \"any Olympic housing\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1847}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, athletes will stay on a nearby boat.\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1894, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1866}, {\"ngram\": \"a nearby boat\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Homes of locals will serve other Olympic housing needs.\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1950, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Homes\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1900}, {\"ngram\": \"locals\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1910}, {\"ngram\": \"other Olympic housing needs\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 1949}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organizers also shrunk the size of the planned structure, a platform, they will build in the ocean.\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 2051, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Organizers\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 1962}, {\"ngram\": \"the size\", \"from\": 1975, \"to\": 1983}, {\"ngram\": \"the planned structure\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 2008}, {\"ngram\": \"a platform\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2020}, {\"ngram\": \"the ocean\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Judges will watch the competition from the platform.\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2104, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Judges\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2058}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2085}, {\"ngram\": \"the platform\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2103}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some people worry that thedrillinginto the reef will disrupt the ecosystem and attract a dangerousalgae.\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2210, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some people\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2117}, {\"ngram\": \"the reef\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2153}, {\"ngram\": \"the ecosystem\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2180}, {\"ngram\": \"a dangerousalgae\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2209}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If fish eat the algae, people who eat the fish can become sick.\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2274, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fish\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2218}, {\"ngram\": \"the algae\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2232}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2240}, {\"ngram\": \"the fish\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2257}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Twenty-two-year-old Mormon Maitei is concerned about the fish in the area.\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2296, \"end\": 2302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mormons\", \"score\": 0.9321022805642835, \"rank\": 0.07187676118436256, \"text\": \"Mormon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mormons\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mormons\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fish\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2337}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maitei is a spearfisher who catches fish to feed his family.\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2411, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Maitei\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2357}, {\"ngram\": \"a spearfisher\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2374}, {\"ngram\": \"fish\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2391}, {\"ngram\": \"his family\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2410}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He sells what they do not need.\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2443, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The water is \\\"where we get our dinner,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2492, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The water\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2453}, {\"ngram\": \"our dinner\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tahitians also worry that changing the reef could also change the shape of the famous waves.\", \"from\": 2494, \"to\": 2586, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2494, \"end\": 2503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahitians\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.70774012778914e-28, \"text\": \"Tahitians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahitians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahitians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the reef\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2537}, {\"ngram\": \"the shape\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2565}, {\"ngram\": \"the famous waves\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Levy said if the reef cracks and breaks off \\\"there will be no more wave over here, it will be finished for us.\\\"\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2699, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Levy\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2592}, {\"ngram\": \"the reef cracks\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2616}, {\"ngram\": \"no more wave\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2659}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2695, \"to\": 2697}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In December, the worries of the locals were confirmed when a boat working on some Olympic construction hit a piece of the reef and broke it.\", \"from\": 2701, \"to\": 2841, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"December\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2712}, {\"ngram\": \"the worries\", \"from\": 2714, \"to\": 2725}, {\"ngram\": \"the locals\", \"from\": 2729, \"to\": 2739}, {\"ngram\": \"a boat\", \"from\": 2760, \"to\": 2766}, {\"ngram\": \"some Olympic construction\", \"from\": 2778, \"to\": 2803}, {\"ngram\": \"a piece\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 2815}, {\"ngram\": \"the reef\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 2827}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cindy Otcenasek, the president of Via Ara o Teahupo'o, called the destruction deeply hurtful.\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2936, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2843, \"end\": 2848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cindy_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.9993580129511742, \"rank\": 0.00064026544509191